{"tid":2143803,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"總統催復課 訛稱兒童難染武肺  打擊假抗疫資訊 fb刪特朗普片段","createTime":"2020-08-07T09:53:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T10:58:02.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"58727320e881f49357cd9541075d41aaa84ef986","tid":2143803,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T09:53:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200807/DA2QQWICVUWWYRFQ2AO3AHK5CA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200807%2FDA2QQWICVUWWYRFQ2AO3AHK5CA%2F&d=ACvVw7CXGjn4pyDVYlJlLHfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=c6d1ed2f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200807%2FDA2QQWICVUWWYRFQ2AO3AHK5CA%2F&h=321c4ffa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200807/DA2QQWICVUWWYRFQ2AO3AHK5CA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n總統催復課 訛稱兒童難染武肺 <br />\n打擊假抗疫資訊 fb刪特朗普片段<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/HDcr5ivZ_iUxukNZMvw6Enk-4OE=/640x400/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4DENQ5DACOS2R4BXRTDLFRHLGA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FHDcr5ivZ_iUxukNZMvw6Enk-4OE%3D%2F640x400%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4DENQ5DACOS2R4BXRTDLFRHLGA.jpg&h=0c496d00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n特朗普受訪稱兒童對武漢肺炎幾乎免疫。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普為提供理據讓學校復課，前日再發放錯誤的疫情資訊，稱兒童「幾乎免疫」於武漢肺炎。社交媒體facebook其後首次以發放假疫情資訊為由刪除該片段，Twitter亦指言論違反打擊假新聞政策，屏蔽相關帖文。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。但一些兒童和嬰兒都染病，能傳染給其他人；美國兒科學會只稱兒童傳染力較低，並非免疫；世界衞生組織統計2月24日至7月12日的600萬宗個案後，亦指5至14歲兒童佔總確診者的4.6%。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTwitter屏蔽相關帖文<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：德銀交出特朗普財務紀錄<br />\n<br />\nfb過往被批打擊仇恨言論和假資訊不力，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普競選團隊的官方Twitter賬戶@TeamTrump亦上載了該影片，隨即被屏敝。Twitter發言人同樣表示影片內容違反打擊假新聞政策，要求賬戶持有人要先刪除該帖子，否則不能再發文。賬戶頁面其後沒有再顯示這段影片，並如常運作。影片平台YouTube亦以相同理由將訪問片段下架，但霍士新聞在平台上的頻道此後仍能看到該影片。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/yxMJNKko7t_I9VqJhCrjTLDf4Cw=/640x460/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2CEEBIV7WYGPUODHNYDCRB22UY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FyxMJNKko7t_I9VqJhCrjTLDf4Cw%3D%2F640x460%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2CEEBIV7WYGPUODHNYDCRB22UY.jpg&h=b04eebc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nfacebook打擊發放疫情虛假資訊。美聯社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n團隊斥社交媒體偏見<br />\n<br />\n面對社交媒體更嚴格審查，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n這段訪問只是特朗普輕視疫情的其中一個例子。他昨日聲稱國內武肺疫苗或可在11月3日大選日前面世；而美國有線新聞網絡（CNN）消息報道，他前日與醫療專家舉行自4月以來首次深度會議，專家在會上說服他要更認真看待疫情，但他仍不明白情況有多嚴重，並多次嘗試轉換話題。白宮反駁報道內容，稱特朗普當時充份參與抗疫工作和聽取匯報。<br />\n<br />\n路透社/法新社/美國有線新聞網絡"},{"pid":"a812ccd420918d60ba4588e5364614ca13eeafa4","tid":2143803,"uid":48631,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T10:02:39.000Z","msg":"連登仔：<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f0/Blue_double_ticks.svg/1280px-Blue_double_ticks.svg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2Ff%2Ff0%2FBlue_double_ticks.svg%2F1280px-Blue_double_ticks.svg.png&h=36f79bcb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"31768d39ea5a1027995d11f2aedeb36811923950","tid":2143803,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T10:03:34.000Z","msg":"唔出奇wo <br />\n香港有幾個多小朋友有中"},{"pid":"68e195e5c8d04d33a4b26872263189fcd151822f","tid":2143803,"uid":30831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31768d39ea5a1027995d11f2aedeb36811923950","tid":2143803,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T10:03:34.000Z","msg":"唔出奇wo <br />\n香港有幾個多小朋友有中"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T10:05:15.000Z","msg":"好似又係幾少聽 定係冇報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hk